<p>Do not just cite other sources. Create your own data when possible. AI engines cannot replicate original research. That makes your content uniquely valuable as a citation source that no competitor can duplicate.</p>
<p>Even simple metrics work. "We analyzed 50 client websites and found X" provides citable original data. Every business generates data worth sharing. Start measuring and documenting your results.</p>
